\begin{frame}{\hspace{3.5cm} Future work  }
\begin{itemize}

 
\item Test the algorithm with the cosmic muons events available in protoDUNE data. 
\item Differentiating upward-going muons from downward-going muons using shower shapes.
\item Perform the analysis with DL (Deep Learning) algorithms as done by the IceCube collaboration. 
\item Systematic uncertainty evaluation. (muon radiation modeling, electronics saturation, recombination modeling in dense showers and electron lifetime).
\end{itemize}
